International career
Sielis was the captain of Cyprus national team under 21,17 with 8 appearances and 2 goals. On 03 September 2010 Sielis scored his first goal with the national team under 21 in a away victory 1-3 over Norway under-21 football team.18
On 26 March 2010, Sielis made his debut with the national team of Cyprus in the home draw 0-0 againsgt Iceland.19 in 2012/13, Sielis played in 2 of national tema matches, in a home victory 1-0 against Iceland, and in away defeat 2-1 from Slovenia.20
